description: Lists all of the policy generations requested in the last seven days.

parameters.name: principalArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the IAM entity (user or role) for which you are generating a policy. Use this with ListGeneratedPolicies to filter the results to only include results for a specific principal.

parameters.name: maxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of results to return in the response.

parameters.name: nextToken
parameters.description: A token used for pagination of results returned.
